<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Kelvin Wiggly｜Morning Brief Home</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@700;900&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,900;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/morning-brief.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/home.css">
</head>
<body>

<header class="masthead">
  <div class="masthead-inner container">
    <div><span class="kw-mark">K</span> Kelvin Wiggly</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <span>首頁</span>
      <a href="/Morning-Brief/water-level.html">｜ 水位紀錄</a>
      <a href="/Morning-Brief/radar-brake.html">｜ 飆股雷達煞車器</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="container" style="padding-top:30px;padding-bottom:72px">
  <header class="home-header">
    <p class="home-eyebrow">Taiwan pre-open decision brief</p>
    <h1>Kelvin Wiggly 每日市場晨報</h1>
    <p class="home-subtitle">以方舟水位為母系統，早上先判斷風險預算，再看主線、換手與調節。這裡整理台股開盤前需要先讀完的市場邊界：水位、主線、風險、以及不追價的操作提醒。</p>
    <div class="home-btns">
      <a class="home-btn primary" href="/Morning-Brief/{{ latest.filename }}">閱讀今日晨報</a>
      <a class="home-btn" href="/Morning-Brief/water-level.html">水位紀錄</a>
      <a class="home-btn" href="/Morning-Brief/radar-brake.html">飆股雷達煞車器</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="grid3">
    <div class="home-card">
      <div class="label">今日水位</div>
      <div class="num">{{ latest.ark.water_level }}%</div>
      <p>{{ home.water_note }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-card">
      <div class="label">今日主線</div>
      <h3>{{ latest.strategy.thesis }}</h3>
      <p>{{ home.thesis_blurb }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-card">
      <div class="label">風險姿態</div>
      <div class="num" style="font-size:1.5rem">{{ latest.market.systemic_risk }}</div>
      <p>{{ home.risk_tagline }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Recent issues</p>
    <h2 class="section-title-home">最近兩日晨報大綱</h2>
    <div class="grid2">
      {%- for item in recent_issues %}
      <a class="recent-card" href="/Morning-Brief/{{ item.filename }}">
        <h3>{{ item.date_display }}｜{{ item.scenario_name }}</h3>
        <p>{{ item.summary }}</p>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top:36px">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Service</p>
    <h2 class="section-title-home">我提供的市場整理方式</h2>
    <div class="grid3">
      <div class="home-card">
        <div class="label">開盤前晨報</div>
        <p>把美股與高權重訊號壓縮成台股可執行的主線、風險與換手觀察。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-card">
        <div class="label">方舟水位紀錄</div>
        <p>保留水位變化，讓每一天的風險預算與調節理由有脈絡可追。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="home-card">
        <div class="label">追價煞車器</div>
        <p>把強勢題材拆成可觀察、等回測、禁止追價三種狀態，避免情緒加速。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="home-footer">
    Kelvin Wiggly｜以水位、位階與紀律為核心的台股開盤前市場整理。
  </footer>
</main>
</body>
</html>
